                            <comment id="16039569" author="svenmeier" created="Tue, 6 Jun 2017 20:28:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is one of the scariest code parts of Wicket, so kudos for tracing this down.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m clearly in favor of following the single most important rule I know about WebPageRenderer: create the page as late as possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll investigate further and would propose to revert to the previous handling, i.e. call isPageStateless() lazily as you have suggested,&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
